{"tid":991122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，其實香港政府部門係唔互通資料架","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T10:31:44.000Z","uid":227801,"like":412,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"264be55848f67a03d7737e690c492edb5a1063c1","tid":991122,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"我唔係話佢今次做得好， 當然係麻煩， 好似上次咁做就最好<br />\n<br />\n但係有一點我想講， 好多人都話&quot;政府&quot;咪有曬我哋資料囉， 做乜仲要再問<br />\n<br />\n但其實呢個&quot;政府&quot;， 係指一個整體， 我哋各部門間係唔會互通資料， 除非你特別向其他部門要個別資料<br />\n<br />\ne.g. Lands冇HAD資料<br />\n        社署冇水記資料<br />\n        如此類推，唔會互通<br />\n<br />\n更加唔會有稅局資料"},{"pid":"2ec5297a4a9cb0652965202b090183e5c8b38b9f","tid":991122,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3535b9cf311a5efc7101929f1658fc509bb1bb","tid":991122,"uid":182499,"like":21,"dislike":25,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"15863b8e2d4deba208295bed8b0e6f75cb0a0d36","tid":991122,"uid":147226,"like":491,"dislike":4,"score":487,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:55:23.000Z","msg":"其實唔只無資料咁簡單<br />\n基本上政府部門之間係唔會講野或者溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15472a2fd1b2132bae36bd6e2841d3f90e93c87a","tid":991122,"uid":172844,"like":287,"dislike":11,"score":276,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"但真心想知要幾百萬人填表寫信去寄快<br />\n定係問另一個部門拎資料快?"},{"pid":"3e824c20ea75ff360879277b61978b0b6a53758d","tid":991122,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:59:01.000Z","msg":"通條毛<br />\n<br />\n改地址都要續個部門改"},{"pid":"4ab5c33702a0f1bbcc214f7b0cd855937d2897ed","tid":991122,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"之前又得？"},{"pid":"20dc5d84ae552031008d72fc549749ca97bb616d","tid":991122,"uid":159879,"like":186,"dislike":